article_title: Federal health insurance marketplace starts much better in SC on second try
article_text: What a difference a year makes. The first week of 2015 enrollment in the federal health insurance marketplace through healthcare.gov was busy and free of major technical problems, according to those who help people enroll in South Carolina.
